        a                 owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "It seems necessary to point out that the K+ efflux through NMDA receptor channels is not an event that takes place in the absence of Ca2+ and Na+; it occurs simultaneously with influx Ca2+ and Na+ into the cell and at similar physiological membrane potentials. have I to add also Na+ and K+?" ;
